➜【感动】“回去再向老板解释”，送水师傅打开纯净水当街倒了……
http://www.sohu.com/a/415944260_115354	15964
<p><span>近日，在陕西旬阳县街头</span></p>
<p><span><strong>送水师傅把客户订的纯净水当街倒了</strong></span></p>
<p><span>这一幕被拍摄上传网络后</span></p>
<p><span>收获一片赞誉</span></p>
<p><span>这是怎么回事</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200901/33e40e5782fa425cac087d09730b6480.png" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>↓↓↓</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>“灭火要紧</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>回去再向老板解释”</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>视频中的这位</span><strong><span>送水师傅名叫罗侯稳</span></strong></p>
<p><span>当天早上，罗师傅在开车送水途中</span></p>
<p><span>行至某眼镜店门前时</span></p>
<p><span>发现</span><strong><span>一辆摩托车正在燃烧</span></strong></p>
<p><span>情急之中</span></p>
<p><span>罗师傅打开一大桶纯净水</span></p>
<p><span>冲向摩托车</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>充足的水量很快压住了火势</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200901/d504fc155acf4326b8f76961db11ee96.gif" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
